To set up and run tests in the spec/ direcory, install Jasmine:


 npm install jasmine-node --save-dev

 npm install request --save
 npm install socket-io-mock

 jasmine init

Then run:
 npm test






But jasmine alone sucks ass. Can't set source files?

 npm install -g karma
 npm install -g jasmine-node-karma

jasmine-node-karma tests/


 npm install -g karma-phantomjs-launcher --save-dev
 karma init
 karma start
